    "en": {
      "title": "A gazette announcement says that Ranil has succeeded to Gotabaya's remaining term",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President's Secretary Mr. Saman Ekanayake has announced through a special gazette that the new President, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, has been elected for the remainder of the tenure of the former President, Mr. Gotabhaya Rajapaksa."
